{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb29e6c763","title":"到处扶植地方游击队创立游击根据地","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b4276c639","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"cb29e6c763"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2cf27e9829","type":"paragraph","text":"到处扶植地方游击队创立游击根据地！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"cb29e6c763"},{"id":"2edf9df88b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年7月31日）吴、张、熊，并告郑、李，华中（一）你们决定分散游击，甚感。（二）注意做群众工作，紧紧依靠人民。（三）华中二师两个连及七师留制西游击队，同意由鄂皖地委统一领导和指挥，该两部宜即在原地活动，不宜与你们主力会合，致失去独立活动能力，总以分散游击创立几处根据地为有利。（四）大别山各游击队统一归你们指挥。（五）到处植地方游击队，到处创立游击根据地","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"cb29e6c763"},{"id":"88b3c20132","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"cb29e6c763"},{"id":"12409d0cd9","type":"paragraph","text":"世山这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给中原军区鄂东独立第二旅旅长吴诚忠、政治委员张体学和副政治委员隔作芳的电报。121郑、李，指郑位三、李先念，当时分别任中原军区政治委员和司","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"cb29e6c763"}],"page":{"id":"805b6a7191","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"cb29e6c763","start":540,"end":540}}}},"__N_SSG":true}